      • toFrames

        public double[] toFrames(double step)
        Convert this sequence of pitch targets into an array of frame values. Values before the first target are NaN, values after the last target are NaN; values between targets are linearly interpolated.
        Parameters:
        step - the constant time distance between two frames, in seconds.
        Returns:
        an array of doubles representing the equally spaced frequency values, from xmin to xmax.
